OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA band of showery rain will
OL,6,Fmove slowly southeast during the
OL,7,Fafternoon, with some showers perhaps
OL,8,Fbecoming locally heavy. Generally
OL,9,Flight winds, with temperatures near
OL,10,Fnormal.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with showers
OL,13,Fpersisting into the evening, with a
OL,14,Ffurther band of rain and showers
OL,15,Fmoving southeastwards during the early
OL,16,Fhours. Winds remain light but blustery
OL,17,Falong the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
