OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA band of rain, heavy at
OL,6,Ftimes continues to move slowly
OL,7,Fsoutheast, overnight could see some
OL,8,Fbreaks in the cloud and ground frost
OL,9,Fpatches forming. Breezy and cooler.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FSunday,
OL,12,Fdry with sunny, winds easing. Monday,
OL,13,Fshowers moving south then brighter and
OL,14,Fcooler. Tuesday sunny intervals in the
OL,15,Fmorning with afternoon showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
